<p>In the event that SCP-3-J ever begins Fucking its Leg, Dr. Bright is to Fuck SCP-3-J until it ceases its behavior. In the event of a containment breach, Mobile Task Force Ω-7 (''Doctor who'') is to be dispatched to SCP-3-J's last known location.</p>
<p>Description: SCP-3-J is a Pinkish Kitten. Like most members of its species, it is able to Fly Fly, and regularly eats twice its own weight in Macaroni each day.</p>
